        <h2 class="marketing-columns">{{#link-to 'artist.quiroz'}}Amanda Quiroz{{/link-to}}</h2>
        <p>Amanda Quiroz is showing drawings at Flickerbox, Inc. June 15 - August 15 2017.</p>
        <p>Amanda Quiroz draws from her personal entomological collection to explore themes of mortality and humility within Catholicism. Her intricate drawings of insects and the very dust from the air seek to illuminate the invisible.</p>
