        <p>Alanna Risse is showing photography at {{#link-to 'venues'}}Red Fox{{/link-to}} in July 2017.</p>
        <p>Alanna Risse is a multi-disciplinary artist and graduate of the Low-Residency MFA in Visual Studies Program at PNCA. She lives in Portland, Oregon with her husband, almost-7-year-old daughter, and dog. Risse's solo exhibition at Red Fox can be seen daily 3pm - 1:30am. 21+ only please. Red Fox is located at 5128 N. Albina, Portland OR.</p>
      </article>
