        <p>Veronica Reeves is showing paintings at {{#link-to 'venues'}}Akemi Salon{{/link-to}} in May 15 - September 15 2017.</p>
        <p>Reeves' solo exhibition "Budding" features new experimentations in watercolors. This is Verge's first exhibition at Akemi Salon. Details for a reception will be posted later this summer. Akemi Salon is located at 3808 N. Williams Ste D, Portland OR.</p>
